public enum Armor

Enum for armor types. Number and names will be hardcoded. People can change absorption amounts.

Author:
Darren Watts date 11/11/07

setStats

public void setStats(java.lang.String itemName,
                     java.lang.String secondName,
                     int absorbMelee,
                     int absorbMartialArts,
                     int absorbMarksman,
                     int absorbFlame,
                     int absorbOther,
                     boolean canBreak)
Sets the absorption stats of this armor. Absorption stats are a percentage of damage absorbed if hit with the specified damage type. For example, if absorbMelee is set to 20, 20% of melee damage will be absorbed by the armor.

Parameters:
itemName - String : item name
secondName - String : secondary name
absorbMelee - int : absorption melee percent
absorbMartialArts - int : absorption martial arts percent.
absorbMarksman - int : absorption marksman percent.
absorbFlame - int : absorption flame percent.
absorbOther - int : absorption other percent.
canBreak - boolean : armor can be destroyed
